headline: ONEOK (OKE) Draws Mixed Analyst Calls and Price Target Falls
summary: ONEOK, Inc. (NYSE:OKE) is one of the 11 Best Pipeline and MLP Stocks to Buy in 2026. Morgan Stanley analyst Robert Kad lowered the price target on ONEOK, Inc.
